## 2026-03-27 - ImportPanel: Handler for `styles-read` message does not clear `pendingSourceRef` before processing
- Fixed `styles-read` handler in `useEffect` message listener: removed `pendingSourceRef.current === 'styles'` from the guard condition (correlationId alone is the authoritative match), and moved `pendingSourceRef.current = null` + `correlationIdRef.current = null` to the very top of the handler body (before `clearTimeout`). This ensures a second `styles-read` response with the same correlationId is processed rather than silently dropped because `pendingSourceRef` was already cleared.
